doing justice to each side return
in the circumstances of some cases
on the campus.
Accordingly, the problem centers
in the conditions and extent of the
accused’s Claim to know the
sources of evidence against him.
In View of two beliefs, I am not
consensus to any absolute prescription. My first belief is, that
various treasures on the individual
may lead to affair compression o!
evidence in ways that in fact sun.
press responsible individual action
and are fundamental to the college. My second belief is, that w.
