border, will be times off in the
earnings. And the thinking lights
will go, too. party said that the
lights will be “classes” once at
five minutes before women's hours
each evening.
On the lower level there will be
some changes, too. The committee
informed its statement that some
light must be present in the dining rooms when they are in use.
but said that candle light would
be satisfactory.
