Carleton's new pool, There are apparently three teams with a shot at
the title — Beloit, Cornell, and Grinnell. The bloggers detected Beloit
and lost to Cornell on a disqualification in dual meets. Conference
meets are a different story, however, and dual meets cannon be used
to predict the outcome. John iraqi, Tony norton, Ken sherman, and
Ralph Pray should lead the Pioneer assault. It will be, in any event,
an exciting meet which could easily be decided at the finals in the
400-yard lifestyle relay. All three of the containers have true teams
in the event and they could ﬁwish within a body length of each other.
