Morgan Michel in the heather weights will have to give the team
needed points. Two Grinnellians who could surprise are Mike Deatherage and Gary Wilson. It is not known whether Wilson is eligible,
for he just transferred back to Grinnell alter a semester at West
Point. At any rate, Cornell, plymouth, Carleton, and Grinnell are
