The track team is traveling to Chicago for its conference meet,
which Grinnell has Won the last three years in a row. Running in the
meet, in addition to the ten conference schools, is the University of
Chicago, which seems to be head and providers above the conference
teams. The Pioneers can still win the conference championship, however, if they can output the Midwest Conference teams and finish second to Chicago. The troops are somewhat reported this season in
numbers, and thus they are only entered in three delays instead of the
usual five. Paul batteries, Steve paintball, John TePaske and Mike
